hcc_text: Guy R Brewer Boulevard is a pedestrian high crash corridor (top third for pedestrian deaths and serious injuries per mile in Queens)
info: At Guy R Brewer Boulevard at 150th Road, 150th Avenue and Rockaway Boulevard, there were 6 deaths and severe injuries in crashes between 2008 and 2012.
